# Forms Rules

## Stack
React Hook Form + Zod + Server Actions

## Validation
- Schema in `lib/validations/contact-form.ts`
- Server-side validation mandatory in Server Action
- Honeypot field `website` must be empty

## Submission
- External endpoint via `CONTACT_FORM_ENDPOINT` env var
- Never store in custom database
- Return `{ success, error }` — no thrown errors to client

## Accessibility
- Visible labels on all inputs
- `aria-invalid` + `aria-describedby` for errors
- `aria-live="polite"` on success

## Security
- Honeypot hidden with `sr-only`, `tabIndex={-1}`, `aria-hidden`
- No PII in logs
- Server Actions for CSRF protection
